Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Spring…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.33,0:00:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A time when everyone\Nsets off for new places{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.64,0:00:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}full of hope in their hearts…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's Spring.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I had long lost any hopes\Nfor the new season.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.39,0:00:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mizuiro?! Where are you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.14,0:00:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Weren't you listening to\Nwhat I said last night?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I told you not to call\Nbecause I'm busy today!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.10,0:00:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Child, you're always like this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You should try putting yourself\Nin my shoes sometimes…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.62,0:00:40.25,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,CALL TIME\N00:04:17
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calling your mother again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.57,0:00:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a good son.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.46,0:00:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go talking\Nlike that again…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.35,0:00:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll make your mother cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Your jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's your school\Nentrance ceremony, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I drive you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.79,0:01:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hello, hello.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.92,0:01:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mizuiro to world.\NCome in world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is our cord connected correctly?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.13,0:01:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My world appears to be\Nspinning correctly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.10,0:01:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All systems green.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.24,0:01:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Communications…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.91,0:01:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}failure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Ichi! Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast time!\NYou'll be late for school!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.09,0:03:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Big Brother,\Nwhat about breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Yuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back before noon,\Nso just leave it there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh pooh!\NI already fried you an egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.93,0:03:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Aizen, may I have\Na moment of your time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure Hinamori, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:05.76,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Endure, no matter what"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It shows your free-flowing style\Nvery well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and this is my report\Nfor the lieutenants meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll look it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto! Are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.78,0:04:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're not here,\Nwhy's this room reek of liquor…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…Captain…\NJoin me for a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But never mind that.\NWhere's your report?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't today\Nthe lieutenants meeting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't fall asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to…me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:05:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that…not there…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For crying out loud…\Nwhat's this woman dreaming about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You haven't started yet?\NThank goodness…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just take your seat and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto hasn't come…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably got a hangover again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kusajishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are sweets I brought,\Nyou know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your "thank you"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mare-rin, the things you say\Nare awfully stingy for a rich guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow ow ow…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your voices boom in my head!\NKeep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, are you nursing a hangover,\Ntoo, Lieutenant Iba?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. This is the best cure\Nfor a hangover.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:17.12,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,KARAKURA FIRST HIGH SCHOOL
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A new uniform…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.74,0:06:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A new school, eh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Guess I should\Nstart feeling like…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How any normal\Nnew students should feel…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, this goes way beyond\Nthe school regulations
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your entire head is bright yellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sado!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasutora Sado!\NAren't you going to say hi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Reiichi Oshima\Nfrom Togata Junior High!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mocking me, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.71,0:07:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You boys there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bug off!\NI've got a beef with this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi…zu…i…ro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-T-Trouble, Mizuiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Keigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to hear this!\NThere's big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:07:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awfully hyper\Nthis morning, Keigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiba Junior High's\NChad and Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems the both of them\Nenrolled in this school!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You…moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.94,0:08:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chad and Kurosaki are pedigreed\Nsuper juvenile delinquents!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That they're in close\Nwith the Yakuza,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.41,0:08:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that they're smuggling in drugs,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that they go into\Nbook stores and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,browse porno for\Nfive hours at a time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dark rumors about them\Nare countless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never met them,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you don't what\Nsort of people they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Chad and Kurosaki\Nwe're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "don't know\Nwhat sort of people they are"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.19,0:08:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}– Let's see…\N– One's a wicked,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}– First, each class assembles\N– orange-haired fighter who dyed his{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}– for a short homeroom, \N– hair from the day he was born, and{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}– followed by the ceremony…\N– the other's a 2-meter-tall giant!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the class assignments\Nare posted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.20,0:08:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it says we're\Nboth in class 1-3.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see that from here?\NYour eyes are pretty good
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:03.09,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,ICHIGO KUROSAKI\NYASUTORA SADO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that must never\Nhappen became reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our youth…just ended…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Hey, that's Kojima.\N– You mean yours did, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Don't you think Kojima\N– We have no tomorrow…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– is sort of hot?\N– You sure exaggerate, man…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– He's like…not overly driven…\N– So long,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– a non-aggressive type, you know.\N– my fresh new high school life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he seems unbothered,\Nyet sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.\NLike he's going to heal you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not driven, only because\NI don't have any expectations.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or any anger…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My smile is nothing\Nmore than a pose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can do it to anyone,\Nanytime, anywhere.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.08,0:10:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see…\NWhere is…Tatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're off guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good, Orihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't catch me\Noff guard anymore…Tatsuki…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.31,0:10:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, you pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've improved your reflexes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you're\Na good teacher, Tatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But please stop with\Nthe surprise attack tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll scare everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon jour, Mademoiselle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Chizuru Honsho, and I have\Nbecome a member of this class.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.91,0:11:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you do that for,\Nyou violent woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what were you planning\Nto do to Orihime?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a lovely name,\Nso appropriate for my new Venus…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said cut it out, you airhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This violence will not\Nmake my love waver!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!\NYou want more, you pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Tatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll end up killing her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought flowers today again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, that man is\Ntalking to the flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that. It's rude to point!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on,\Nwhat's really bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well you see…\Nsomething's odd…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:12:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something about the sky is odd…\Nand I'm afraid…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Afraid of… the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the matter, Karin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be late for school!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it start raining or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm really not sure, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky seems heavy somehow…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the usual old person again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're wondering about him,\Nhe's right next you, Yuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're kidding, right?\NWhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, is the matter of\Nthe vacancy position of
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a Konpaku Monitoring Officer\Nstationed at 3600
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on the World of the Living axis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, a member from our\Nsquad is in charge of this area,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he has been\Non extended absence
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,due to a worsening\Nof his chronic cramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! A swift kick to the back\Nwill fix that up right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:13:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, cramps are painful…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to let him rest…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.83,0:13:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Sasakibe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to recommend\NRukia Kuchiki from our squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your reasons?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some time now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Ukitake has\Nwanted to place Kuchiki
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in a stationed officer position\Nin the World of Living
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to gain experience\Nas a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, Captain Ukitake\Nrecommended her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia Kuchiki of Squad 13\Nwill be the replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proceed to the next matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. In regard to the vacancy\Nposition of lieutenant of Squad 6,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Captain's Meeting has chosen
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Renji Abarai,\NSixth Seat of Squad 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy's a punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy serving as lieutenant,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will scar the name of\Nthe Thirteen Court Guard Squads!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mare-rin's bald head\Nwill be scarred, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not bald,\Nand I won't be scarred!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these…orders of transfer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing so serious as a "transfer"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's resident officer duty\Nin the World of the Living!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You remember, a long time ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you first joined us,\Nyou came along to assist me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember? That's all it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, she doesn't remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a bad experience,\Nso she erased it from her brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kuchiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're bothering us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you stay\Nburied in the garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! And why don't you just go\Nhang yourself from the eaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your resident duty station\Nis one Reiri radius area
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a town called Karakura\Nat the center…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It shouldn't be that difficult\Nof an assignment
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with your level of skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Ukitake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't be up!\NYou need to rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was feeling\Nbetter today, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And even though it's a short\Nassignment of about a month,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Kuchiki might\Nhave some anxieties
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.59,0:15:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about her first solo\Nresident officer assignment,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I came to see her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop with the formalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you told Byakuya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! No, not yet…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…no…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kuchiki\Nwill no doubt say…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't report to me each time\Nabout something so minor."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I plan to leave\Nwithout letting him know…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.35,0:15:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.06,0:15:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's how you feel,\Nthat's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let Byakuya know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can leave rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, Renji Abarai,\NSixth Seat of Squad 11
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.74,0:16:10.21,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,LETTER OF APPOINTMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.74,0:16:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is appointed lieutenant\N	of Squad 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Abarai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I humbly accept,\NLieutenant Hinamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be so formal…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, well…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're a step closer again\Nto Byakuya Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikkaku…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it about time already…\Nthat you told your friend Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of whether\Nshe's nobility now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a lieutenant,\Nyou're more than equals…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.24,0:16:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You worked hard for 40 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say it's about time\Nthings return to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the way they were\Nbetween you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'd better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe Kuchiki is\Nleaving in the afternoon
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the World of the Living for\Na month of resident officer duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:17:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Abarari, let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not officially appointed until
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the appointment ceremony\Na month from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When she comes back,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pop the news that I've become\Na lieutenant and surprise her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My rosy youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.29,0:17:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Why did this\Nhave to happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chad and Kurosaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What's is this?\NThis can't be right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This unbelievable\Nway we're getting
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.15,0:17:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sucked in to this\Ncan't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a nightmare?\NCould it be a nightmare?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too noisy…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think you could get away,\NKurosaki…Chad…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Reiichi Oshima from\NTogata Junior High!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Keigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How're you so informed\Nabout delinquent types?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And just so you know, their names\Nwere all on our class roster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you supposed to be?\NAre you with Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've never seen or met\Neach other before now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mizuiro Kojima from\NHiiragi Second Junior High.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in class 1-3.\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.95,0:18:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations,\NMizuiro Kojima has joined his side!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.06,0:18:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No he hasn't. No he hasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuiro! Mizuiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?\NCome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.96,0:18:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not that kind of kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuiro! Mizuiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Class 1-3?\N– Hey, are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– I'm in 1-3, too.\N– Mizuiro! Master Mizuiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– I'm Ichigo Kurosaki\N– Mizuiro-poo! Mizuiro-boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this big guy is Yasutora Sado.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, could you not\Nstep on me there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.81,0:18:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.93,0:18:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, could someone help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– And who's that?\N– Please? Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:18:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Keigo Asano.\N– Mizuiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't do well in school,\Nbut he's a bright guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.65,0:19:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's likable and doesn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a hundred times\Nbetter than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean…I think it's pretty rare\Nfor someone who could
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,say so many nice things\Nabout his friend, when asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kojima, are you good at excuses?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.92,0:19:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so good it's sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then think one up in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A really good one that won't get us
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nsuspended even if we rescue Asano!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who shall I tell of this joy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.47,0:19:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were different\Nthan what we imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm…yeah, maybe they were…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How different were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometimes I think…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're all connected to this world\Nwith countless cords.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And like the patient\Nin intensive care,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.72,0:20:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we desperately try to\Nnot cut even one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the truth is, \Nno matter how hard we try, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they break at the point\Nthey're connected.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to\Ncall Nanako today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's difficult to reattach the cord\Nto its original location…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I still can't do it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hello, hello?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Calling the new world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm glad I met you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does it appear our cords\Nwill connect properly?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is my world spinning properly?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}System: all red.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Communications:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes…\NI sense a powerful Spirit Energy…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AND SO, THE BLADE IS SWUNG
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.11,0:23:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abarai, I hear you're\Ngoing to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.48,0:23:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have work to do, so I can't go,\Nbut I want you to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,get some photos in my place\Nfor the Seireitei Bulletin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.12,0:23:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of Rangiku in a swimsuit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.29,0:23:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say that…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.42,0:23:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– You don't want them?\N– Please get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've just said so\Nat the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.57,0:23:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In today's segment we'll cover\NRangiku Matsumoto's Haineko.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.29,0:23:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Growl, Haineko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.43,0:23:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haineko's power lies in the way\Nthe sword turns into ashes,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.50,0:23:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which then slice to pieces\Nanything that they land on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.38,0:23:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a single swing of the hilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.30,0:23:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a powerful Zanpakuto,\Nbut as Matsumoto puts it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.45,0:23:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it is a very petulant,\Nlazy and stupid sword
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.75,0:23:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that is difficult to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.72,0:24:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really has a mind of its own…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.58,0:24:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could it have taken after?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.40,0:24:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it quite obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.09,0:24:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,